text: Alexander Cairns (23 April 1850 - 16 June 1936) was a New Zealand cricketer. He played three first-class matches for Otago between 1867 and 1871. ==See also== * List of Otago representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1850 births Category:1936 deaths Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Otago cricketers Category:New Zealand people of Scottish descent
